I"¢<h2>When can I see the show?</h2>
<p>20:00-22:00 @ <a href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=bbar+plymouth&amp;rlz=1C5CHFA_enGB844GB844&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjIqIrH6t_iAhUMmxQKHY6IBmIQ_AUIECgB" title="Get directions">The BBar, Barbican Theatre, Plymouth</a>.</p>

<p>Come and see an evening of magical entertainment in Plymouth, comedy and mystery entertainment. Free entry for all first come and first served. Grab some noodles and enjoy the show.</p>

<p>The acts are always a surprise and we do our best to get a new performer each time. If we can't find a new performer then we do make sure to add new material in. Even if you've come before then please visit again.</p>

<p>News can be found on the BBar facebook events page.</p>

<p>You can also see the shows <a href="https://www.b-bar.co.uk/search/label/What%27s%20On" title="Check B-bar events page">listed on their website</a>Â nearer the time.</p>
